Rating: 4
Yummy! I did substitute. I used 1 1/2 c half and half with 4 egg yolks and used bottled vanilla bean paste. It is so good! I am fearful of overcooking the custard and turning it into scrambled eggs so it took me more than 10 minutes to get it to coat the back of a wooden spoon.

