Rating: 4
This was my first attempt at a custard sauce. It was very quick and easy to make, and was a big hit. I served with a three berry cake. I used 1 of Penzy's Madagascar whole vanilla beans and couldn't belive the incredible vanilla flavor! It is worth spending extra for good vanilla for this one.